title: JigSaw v.2.0.12 (astrology software)
description:
JigSaw is a powerful astrological research tool designed to reveal the big picture in any group of charts. JigSaw v. 2.1 is divided into three sections: Family Patterns, Rectification and Research. Each section is composed of a distinct and different set of tools created for examining the astrological relationships between people and life. Jigsaw is a powerful and fun-to-use program that enables you to find the connecting links in large or small groups of horoscopes.

Although a standalone program it can import data from different astrology software.

An update to v2.0.17 is available on Alabe's update page.
